## Consumer Scaling — Configuração Dinâmica

```java
@Configuration
public class RabbitListenerConfig {

    @Bean
    public SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory rabbitListenerContainerFactory(
            ConnectionFactory connectionFactory) {

        SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory factory = new SimpleRabbitListenerContainerFactory();
        factory.setConnectionFactory(connectionFactory);
        factory.setAcknowledgeMode(AcknowledgeMode.MANUAL);
        factory.setPrefetchCount(10);
        factory.setConcurrentConsumers(3);      // consumidores iniciais
        factory.setMaxConcurrentConsumers(20);  // escala até 20 sob carga

        // Reduz consumidores em ociosidade
        factory.setConsumerStartTimeout(60_000L);

        // Métricas com Micrometer
        factory.setMicrometerEnabled(true);

        return factory;
    }
}
```

